Package: bcrm
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian continuous reasssessment method (CRM) designs for Phase
        I dose-finding trials.
Version: 0.1
Date: 2012-01-10
Author: Michael Sweeting <michael.sweeting@mrc-bsu.cam.ac.uk>
Maintainer: Michael Sweeting <michael.sweeting@mrc-bsu.cam.ac.uk>
Description: This package implements a wide variety of one and
        two-parameter Bayesian CRM designs. The program can run
        interactively, allowing the user to enter outcomes after each
        cohort has been recruited, or via simulation to assess
        operating characteristics.
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyLoad: yes
Depends: mvtnorm, ggplot2
Suggests: R2WinBUGS, BRugs
